<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued February 22 at 3:01AM MST until February 24 at 5:00AM MST by NWS GrandJunction</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 5 PM THIS AFTERNOON TO
5 AM MST THURSDAY...
* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of 2 to 4
inches.
* WHERE...Grand Valley.
* WHEN...From 5 PM this afternoon to 5 AM MST Thursday.
* IMPACTS...Travel could become difficult. A detailed map of the
snowfall can be found at: www.weather.gov/gjt/winter.</description>
<instruction>Slow down and use caution while traveling.
The latest road conditions for the state you are calling from can
be obtained by calling 5 1 1.</instruction>
